{"tid":109201,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 魯芬今晨肺部衰竭離世 終年63歲","createTime":"2017-02-05T19:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T20:12:48.000Z","uid":27856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9852ca84d708eb0a81e305bcde1e3f55b41f3aeb","tid":109201,"uid":27856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:50:08.000Z","msg":"本月2日，63歲魯芬因皮肌炎，免疫系出問題致留院，還需插喉，甚至已認不得人。同日魯芬致電回覆本報報平安稱：「多謝，有心。身體健康！」又稱現時「暫時情況OK，多謝關心。」並謂對於好友關心表示感激，笑稱：「哈哈，好有愛啊，感恩！」<br />\n<br />\n豈料事隔不足一周，突傳魯芬病逝消息，令人惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨3時許，魯芬家人發聲明，證實魯芬死訊。全文如下:<br />\n<br />\n「魯芬BB因皮肌炎導致肺部衰竭，於今日凌晨時分在家人朋友陪同下安詳離世，終年63歲。<br />\n<br />\n魯芬BB於十個月前患上皮肌炎，從得知自己患病後，她都一直勇敢面對，對戰勝病魔充滿積極樂觀態度。<br />\n<br />\n感恩各界的愛與關懷，適時公布喪禮安排。<br />\n<br />\n願魯芬BB早往佛國淨土。喃嘸阿彌陀佛！<br />\n<br />\n魯芬BB的家人字<br />\n6/2/2017」<br />\n<br />\n烈火奶奶，一路好走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係掛，咁突然？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170206&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=56266639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170206%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D56266639&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e4a737d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170206%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D56266639&h=f52ce747\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170206&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=56266639</a>"},{"pid":"9669512caa4c60d26fa2c6f49e536faa10623869","tid":109201,"uid":16681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:55:42.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc14aa641ad8795c466171aadfd03831f1a0517","tid":109201,"uid":36,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla